    "description": "GMO Product Platform, Inc. provides an audience engagement platform in Japan, Asia, and internationally. It engages in Internet-based market research activities, conducting surveys, tabulation, and analysis activities. The company also offers ASIACloud Panel, which provides a range of solutions from DIY survey tools to professional research platforms; GMOMarketObserver, a self-service online survey platform; GMOAsk, a packaged survey service utilizing artificial intelligence; GMOCustomer Satisfaction Ranking, which analyzes and publishes user satisfaction feedback; and DepthX by GMO, an AI-powered research module for deeper behavioral insights. In addition, the company offers advertising services that are delivered through proprietary smartphone applications such as TownWiFi by GMO, Cashmart by GMO, and Shift Notebook by GMO. The company was formerly known as GMO Research & AI, Inc. and changed its name to GMO Product Platform, Inc. in October 2025. GMO Product Platform, Inc. was incorporated in 2002 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan. GMO Product Platform, Inc. is a subsidiary of GMO Internet Group, Inc."
